    <p>Please answer truthfully. None of the information you provide in this quiz is used for any purpose other than to pre-screen
        you as an applicant. This helps people who do not qualify from having to go through the application process only
        to be denied several weeks later.</p>
    <p>If you do not submit your answers at the end, we will receive none of your personal information. If you do not qualify
        you will have no option to submit.</p>
